            "body": "The documentation for `WinNew` says:\n```\n\t\t\t\tBefore WinEnter.\n```\nwhile the documentation for `WinEnter` says:\n```\n\t\t\t\tNote: For split and tabpage commands the\n\t\t\t\tWinEnter event is triggered after the split\n\t\t\t\tor tab command but before the file is loaded.\n```\nso `WinNew` is also triggered before the file is loaded, and the file name is not available.",
